    <item>
      <title>多头退却，美元自 2 月以来的最佳涨势受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/dollar-s-best-streak-since-february-threatened-as-bulls-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管受美联储长期维持高利率政策（该政策与全球其他货币政策有所不同）的推动，美元有望创下自 2 月份以来的最佳周度涨幅，但外汇交易员押注美国收益率优势不会持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/dollar-s-best-streak-since-february-threatened-as-bulls-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 11:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙竞选致法国股市遭遇多年来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/macron-election-call-sends-french-markets-to-worst-week-in-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者迅速对法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙提前举行大选的决定表示谴责，因为这引发了人们对法国财政状况进一步恶化的警告，甚至引发了对新一轮欧元危机的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/macron-election-call-sends-french-markets-to-worst-week-in-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 09:53:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
